CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FShe said: "I was singing to her and
OL,7,Fshe was rubbing my face and then she
OL,8,Fhad her final seizure in my arms. They
OL,9,Ftook her off me and put her in the
OL,10,FICU. It was two days before her
OL,11,Fbirthday. I've still got her presents
OL,12,Fwrapped up."
OL,14,FIn the weeks and months that followed,
OL,15,FLoren turned to 'Love Jasmine', a
OL,16,Fcharity which provides bereavement
OL,17,Fsupport for families who have lost a
OL,18,Fchild.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FShe said: "It's a lifeline to me. I'd
OL,7,Fbe lost without them. If you haven't
OL,8,Flost a child you'll never understand
OL,9,Fthis pain. Parents know how you feel,
OL,10,Fyou grieve together, it doesn't take
OL,11,Fthe pain away, but it does make it a
OL,12,Flittle bit better."
OL,14,FThe charity was set up in 2016 Rob and
OL,15,FKathy Lapsley, after they lost their
OL,16,Fdaughter Jasmine aged six - to provide
OL,17,Fbetter support than what was available
OL,18,Fto them in Merseyside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FLove Jasmine offers counselling, peer
OL,7,Fsupport and children's therapy to
OL,8,Ffamilies who have lost a child at any
OL,9,Fage, or are facing a terminal
OL,10,Fdiagnosis.
OL,12,FHowever, the future of the service is
OL,13,Fnow in doubt, as they have lost their
OL,14,FNational Lottery funding, leaving them
OL,15,Fwith a #90,000 deficit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FRob said: "If we don't scale back now
OL,7,Fwe'll probably have to close by
OL,8,FChristmas. We're really really hopeful
OL,9,Fit doesn't come to that, we'll do
OL,10,Feverything we can to make sure it
OL,11,Fdoesn't, but that's the reality of it.
OL,13,F"The National Lottery funding was just
OL,14,Fcritical for us, it was a lot of
OL,15,Fmoney."
OL,17,FAround 300 families use the service
OL,18,Fevery year, with most referrals coming
OL,19,Ffrom the NHS, despite not receiving
OL,20,Ffunding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
