OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FRob said: "I never ever thought we'd
OL,7,Fbe in the position where we'd have to
OL,8,Fsay no to somebody, and I find that
OL,9,Fdifficult."
OL,11,FThe couple had applied for continuity
OL,12,Ffunding as their funding from the
OL,13,FNational Lottery Reaching Communities
OL,14,FFund lasts until July, but they were
OL,15,Funsuccessful due to a criteria change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FKathy said: "If this support goes,
OL,7,F(families) are going to go back in the
OL,8,Fsystem, they're going to be lost in
OL,9,Fthe system and they may not access any
OL,10,Fother support. That's going to be
OL,11,Freally detrimental going forward."
OL,13,FJasmine's parents are concerned that
OL,14,Ftheir daughter's legacy is now in
OL,15,Fdoubt, ahead of the 10 year
OL,16,Fanniversary of the charity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
