CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778058353
OL,3,CLove Jasmine: Parent's plea for
OL,4,Cfunding for bereaved families charity
OL,6,FRob said: "This is how I remember her,
OL,7,Fthis is how I honour her memory, I get
OL,8,Fto say her name everyday. To be able
OL,9,Fto do that and support other families
OL,10,Fin her name, I don't take that for
OL,11,Fgranted.
OL,13,F"She was a wonderful little girl and
OL,14,Fjust to keep her memory alive, that's
OL,15,Fa really big deal."
OL,17,FLoren said she "doesn't know what
OL,18,Fshe's going to do" without the charity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
